(24, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Multicolor Half Moon Male HM-BL-28042026-010', 'bet-260428-8953-6673', 'Stunning Halfmoon Betta with long, flowing fins and rich multicolor patterns. Full 180-degree tail spread with strong symmetry—perfect for premium aquascape displays./Collector', 'The Halfmoon Multicolor Long Fin Betta is a striking example of elegance and selective breeding, prized for its perfectly spread 180-degree halfmoon tail and beautifully flowing long fins. Each movement reveals a dynamic blend of colors—ranging from deep iridescent tones to vibrant contrasting hues—creating a living piece of art in motion.\r\n\r\nCarefully bred for both symmetry and finnage quality, this betta displays strong structure, balanced proportions, and smooth fin extension. The multicolor pattern is uniquely distributed, ensuring that no two fish are ever exactly alike—making each individual truly exclusive.\r\n\r\nThis variety thrives best in a calm, well-maintained environment, with clean water conditions and minimal strong currents to protect its delicate long fins. Providing tannin-rich water (such as Indian almond leaves) can help enhance coloration and support natural behavior.\r\n\r\nThe Halfmoon Betta is naturally territorial and solitary, best kept alone or with visual stimulation from nearby tanks. When properly cared for, it will display its full finnage and personality—flaring with confidence and grace.\r\n\r\nPerfect for collectors, aquascape enthusiasts, and international buyers, this fish represents a balance of beauty, genetics, and presentation quality.\r\nYou will receive the exact fish shown in the listing.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Other / Custom', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'thai', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/24/seller_24_20260428070823_ad708eee930e.jpg', 'Halfmoon Long Fin Multicolor Betta Fish | Premium 180° Tail Show Grade', 'Stunning Halfmoon Betta with long flowing fins and vivid multicolor patterns. 180° tail, premium grade, and carefully conditioned. Perfect for collectors and display tanks.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-28 07:08:23', '2026-04-28 07:08:23'),
