 Fish | Premium 180° Tail Show Grade', 'Premium Halfmoon Long Fin Multicolor Betta with a perfect 180° tail spread. Vibrant colors, strong symmetry, and show-quality finnage. Healthy and ready for worldwide shipping.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-28 07:30:15', '2026-04-28 08:32:05'),
