(32, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Multicolor Dombo Big Ear Male HM-BL-28042026-017', 'bet-260428-1519-6918', 'Big Ear (Dumbo) Fancy Betta – premium short-fin betta with oversized pectoral fins, graceful movement, vibrant colors, and strong genetics. A unique show-quality fish perfect for collectors and international buyers.', 'The Big Ear (Dumbo) Fancy Betta is one of the most distinctive and visually captivating varieties of Betta splendens, renowned for its oversized pectoral fins that resemble elephant ears. These elegant fins create a graceful, flowing swimming motion that sets this betta apart from traditional types.\r\n\r\nCarefully bred through selective genetics, this fancy strain combines symmetry, vibrant coloration, and strong fin structure, making it highly desirable among collectors, breeders, and international ornamental fish markets.\r\n\r\nOversized “Big Ear” Pectoral Fins – Signature Dumbo trait with smooth, wing-like movement', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Fancy Multicolor', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/32/seller_32_20260428074516_456e91718f98.jpg', 'Big Ear Dumbo Betta Fish (Fancy Short Fin) – Premium Show Quality for Sale', 'Premium Big Ear Dumbo Betta (Fancy Short Fin) with oversized fins, vibrant colors, and strong genetics. Ideal for collectors, breeders, and international buyers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-28 07:45:16', '2026-05-02 19:45:38'),
(33, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Lavender Dombo Big Ear Male HM-BL-28042026-017', 'bet-260428-9567-4659', 'Big Ear Dumbo Betta (Fancy Short Fin) – high-quality betta fish with large ear-like fins, vivid coloration, and elegant swimming style. Ideal for collectors, breeders, and export-grade markets.', 'The Big Ear (Dumbo) Fancy Betta is one of the most distinctive and visually captivating varieties of Betta splendens, renowned for its oversized pectoral fins that resemble elephant ears. These elegant fins create a graceful, flowing swimming motion that sets this betta apart from traditional types.\r\n\r\nCarefully bred through selective genetics, this fancy strain combines symmetry, vibrant coloration, and strong fin structure, making it highly desirable among collectors, breeders, and international ornamental fish markets.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Other / Custom', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, NULL, 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/33/seller_33_20260428075746_867b96510a77.jpg', 'Big Ear Betta (Dumbo) Fancy Short Fin – High Quality Betta Fish for Sale', 'Big Ear Dumbo Betta fish for sale – high-quality fancy short fin betta with large pectoral fins, vivid colors, and show-grade genetics. Export-ready ornamental fish.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-28 07:57:46', '2026-05-02 19:44:52'),
(34, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light  Male HM-BL-04052026-001', 'bet-260504-7504-6559', 'Headline: Majestic Fantasy Dumbo Ear Betta Fish with Iridescent Pastel Fins\r\nDescription: Own a living piece of art with this stunning Fancy Dumbo Ear Betta Fish. Also known as a Big Ear Betta, this variety features captivating, oversized pectoral fins. T', 'Exquisite Fancy Halfmoon Betta Fish\r\nProduct Overview\r\nElevate your aquarium with the breathtaking beauty of the Fancy Halfmoon . Captured in IMG_0009.jpg, this premium specimen showcases a stunning 180-degree Halfmoon tail combined with the iconic \"Elephant Ears\" (Dumbo) pectoral fins. Its unique Pastel Fancy coloration features a soft, iridescent blend of cream, copper, and sky blue tones, making it a rare find for serious collectors and hobbyists alike.\r\n\r\nDetailed Specifications\r\nVariety: Halfmoon Dumbo Ear (Big Ear)\r\n\r\nColor Pattern: Fancy Pastel / Iridescent Multicolored\r\n\r\nGender: Male\r\n\r\nTemperament: Territorial (Solitary)\r\n\r\nVisual Features: Large, petal-like pectoral fins and a perfectly symmetrical caudal fin spread.\r\n\r\nEssential Betta Fish Care Guide\r\nTo maintain the vibrant colors and long, flowing fins seen in IMG_0009.jpg, proper care is vital. Follow these expert guidelines:\r\n\r\n1. Ideal Tank Setup\r\nMinimum Tank Size: At least 5 gallons (19 liters) to allow for swimming space and stable water parameters.\r\n\r\nFiltration: Use a low-flow filter (sponge filters are best). Halfmoon bettas have heavy fins and struggle to swim against strong currents.\r\n\r\nHeating: Maintain a consistent temperature between 24-28°C (75-82°F) using a reliable aquarium heater.\r\n\r\n2. Water Quality & Maintenance\r\nWater Changes: Perform a 25-30% water change weekly to remove nitrates and ammonia.\r\n\r\nConditioning: Always use a water conditioner to remove chlorine and heavy metals from tap water.\r\n\r\nNatural Tannins: Adding Indian Almond Leaves (Catappa) is highly recommended to boost the immune system and mimic their natural habitat.\r\n\r\n3. Diet and Nutrition\r\nHigh-Protein Diet: Feed high-quality Betta pellets or flakes as a staple.\r\n\r\nVariety: Supplement with frozen or live foods such as Bloodworms, Brine Shrimp, or Daphnia to enhance the iridescent colors seen in IMG_0009.jpg.\r\n\r\nFrequency: Feed small amounts twice daily. Do not overfeed, as this leads to bloating and water spoilage.\r\n\r\n4. Enrichment & Decoration\r\nSafe Plants: Use live plants (Anubias, Java Fern) or silk plants. Avoid plastic plants with sharp edges that can tear delicate Halfmoon fins.\r\n\r\nHiding Spots: Provide a \"Betta log\" or caves so the fish can rest and feel secure.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Yellow', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/34/seller_34_20260504110231_3c2e59385c53.jpg', 'Buy Premium Fancy Halfmoon Betta Fish - Rare Pastel Colors | Bettasociety', 'Discover the beauty of the Fancy Halfmoon Dumbo Ear Betta. Learn expert care tips to maintain their vibrant iridescent colors and majestic fins as seen in Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light  Male HM-BL-04052026-001.jpg. Shop our premium collection of ra', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-04 11:02:31', '2026-05-04 11:02:31'),
(35, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light Marble Male HM-BL-04052026-002', 'bet-260504-9500-8915', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta with soft pastel tones and translucent flowing fins. A rare and elegant ornamental fish perfect for collectors and aquascape displays.', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish – Elegant, Rare, and Collector Grade\r\n\r\nThis stunning Halfmoon Light Marble Betta features a soft pastel coloration with a unique marble pattern that evolves over time, making each fish truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nThe fins are wide and gracefully extended in a full 180-degree Halfmoon spread, showcasing a delicate translucent texture with subtle hints of red and iridescent undertones. Its clean body tone combined with artistic color dispersion creates a premium aesthetic highly sought after in the international betta market.\r\n\r\n✨ Key Features:\r\n\r\nPremium Halfmoon tail with near-perfect spread\r\nLight Marble pattern (color-changing genetics)\r\nSoft pastel / milky white base with artistic accents\r\nSmooth body structure and balanced proportions\r\nIdeal for collectors, breeders, and aquascape displays\r\n\r\n???? This type of betta is especially popular in global markets due to its elegant appearance and unique, ever-changing coloration.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Marble', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/35/seller_35_20260504135355_1bb5aa4ae288.jpg', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish for Sale | Rare Pastel Marble Siamese Fighting Fish', 'Buy Halfmoon Light Marble Betta fish with soft pastel colors and unique marble patterns. Rare, elegant, and perfect for collectors worldwide. Shop premium bettas now.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-04 13:53:55', '2026-05-04 13:53:56'),
(36, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light Marble Male HM-BL-04052026-003', 'bet-260504-7577-2855', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta with soft pastel tones and translucent flowing fins. A rare and elegant ornamental fish perfect for collectors and aquascape displays.', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish – Elegant, Rare, and Collector Grade\r\n\r\nThis stunning Halfmoon Light Marble Betta features a soft pastel coloration with a unique marble pattern that evolves over time, making each fish truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nThe fins are wide and gracefully extended in a full 180-degree Halfmoon spread, showcasing a delicate translucent texture with subtle hints of red and iridescent undertones. Its clean body tone combined with artistic color dispersion creates a premium aesthetic highly sought after in the international betta market.\r\n\r\n✨ Key Features:\r\n\r\nPremium Halfmoon tail with near-perfect spread\r\nLight Marble pattern (color-changing genetics)\r\nSoft pastel / milky white base with artistic accents\r\nSmooth body structure and balanced proportions\r\nIdeal for collectors, breeders, and aquascape displays\r\n\r\n???? This type of betta is especially popular in global markets due to its elegant appearance and unique, ever-changing coloration.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Marble', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/36/seller_36_20260504182436_d4f82ebe8790.jpg', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish for Sale | Rare Pastel Marble Siamese Fighting Fish', 'Buy Halfmoon Light Marble Betta fish with soft pastel colors and unique marble patterns. Rare, elegant, and perfect for collectors worldwide. Shop premium bettas now.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-04 18:24:35', '2026-05-04 18:24:36'),
(37, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light Marble Male HM-BL-04052026-004', 'bet-260504-4009-6403', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta with soft pastel tones and translucent flowing fins. A rare and elegant ornamental fish perfect for collectors and aquascape displays.', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish – Elegant, Rare, and Collector Grade\r\n\r\nThis stunning Halfmoon Light Marble Betta features a soft pastel coloration with a unique marble pattern that evolves over time, making each fish truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nThe fins are wide and gracefully extended in a full 180-degree Halfmoon spread, showcasing a delicate translucent texture with subtle hints of red and iridescent undertones. Its clean body tone combined with artistic color dispersion creates a premium aesthetic highly sought after in the international betta market.\r\n\r\n✨ Key Features:\r\n\r\nPremium Halfmoon tail with near-perfect spread\r\nLight Marble pattern (color-changing genetics)\r\nSoft pastel / milky white base with artistic accents\r\nSmooth body structure and balanced proportions\r\nIdeal for collectors, breeders, and aquascape displays\r\n\r\n???? This type of betta is especially popular in global markets due to its elegant appearance and unique, ever-changing coloration.', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Marble', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Normal', 39.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/37/seller_37_20260504191812_247697eca4d0.jpg', 'Halfmoon Light Marble Betta Fish for Sale | Rare Pastel Marble Siamese Fighting Fish', 'Buy Halfmoon Light Marble Betta fish with soft pastel colors and unique marble patterns. Rare, elegant, and perfect for collectors worldwide. Shop premium bettas now.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-04 19:18:12', '2026-05-04 19:18:13'),
(38, 5, 'Betta Spendens Fancy Half Moon Light Marble Male HM-BL-12052026-001', 'bet-260512-5368-8076', 'Elegant Halfmoon Betta Fish featuring a soft pastel pearl body with shimmering ice blue and peach highlights. This long-fin male displays a wide 180-degree tail spread with flowing fins and delicate color transitions, creating a luxurious and graceful app', 'This stunning Halfmoon Betta Fish showcases an exceptional blend of soft pastel tones, combining pearl white, icy blue, and subtle peach hues into one elegant presentation. Its clean body coloration and refined finnage create a luxurious aesthetic highly sought after in the international betta market.\r\n\r\nThe fish features a beautifully balanced Halfmoon tail with long flowing fins that spread dramatically when fully flared. The translucent layers of the fins reflect light softly, producing an almost silk-like effect underwater. Delicate peach accents along the ventral and lower fins add warmth and contrast without overpowering the fish’s clean pastel appearance.\r\n\r\nIts smooth body structure, symmetrical finnage, and gentle iridescence make this betta an excellent choice for:\r\n\r\nPremium betta collectors\r\nLuxury aquascape displays\r\nBetta competition enthusiasts\r\nFuture breeding projects for pastel and pearl strains\r\n\r\nThis type of pastel Halfmoon Betta is becoming increasingly popular worldwide due to its calm, elegant, and high-end visual appeal. Unlike aggressively colored strains, this fish delivers a refined beauty that stands out through softness, balance, and sophistication.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n\r\nHalfmoon Long Fin Betta\r\nPearl white body with ice blue iridescence\r\nSoft peach pastel accents\r\nWide tail spread and flowing fins\r\nClean structure and elegant symmetry\r\nIdeal for collectors and breeders\r\n\r\nA true luxury betta fish with a graceful presence and rare pastel coloration that captures attention instantly. ✨', 'Betta splendens (Domestic / Fancy)', 'Fancy Light', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'Show Grade', 49.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chiang Mai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '/uploads/listings/38/seller_38_20260512100155_a42bbbfa8e43.jpg', 'Luxury Pastel Halfmoon Betta Fish | Pearl White & Ice Blue Long Fin Betta', 'Explore this stunning Luxury Pastel Halfmoon Betta Fish featuring pearl white coloration, ice blue iridescence, and flowing long fins. A premium ornamental betta perfect for collectors, aquascapes, and high-end breeding projects.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-12 10:01:55', '2026-05-12 10:01:55'),
