(41, 15, 'Pair Live Betta Fish Hybrid Alien Copper Premium Grade Male Female Wild', 'pai-260517-2214-7575', 'Pair Hybrid Alien Copper Betta Fish Male Female M&F Show Quality Live Betta, Get this premium M&F Hybrid Alien Copper Betta pair. Healthy, active, and selected from top breeders. Safe shipping with live arrival guarantee. Don\'t miss this unique pair!', '⚠️ IMPORTANT: PLEASE READ BEFORE BIDDING/BUYING\r\nInternational live fish shipping requires a licensed Transhipper in your country. By buying/bidding, \r\nyou agree to these shipping terms.\r\n\r\nThere will be 2 separate shipping charges:\r\n1.To Seller ($5.00 USD): Covers export fees from Thailand to your country\'s transhipper.\r\n2.To Transhipper ($25.00 - $50.00 USD): Covers customs clearance, import tax, and domestic delivery to your home. \r\n(Paid directly to your transhipper via email invoice—NOT through seller).\r\n\r\nHow it works:\r\n1.You buy the fish + provide your Email Address (for the fish bag label).\r\n2.We ship the fish to the Transhipper in your country.\r\n3.Your Transhipper sends you an invoice for domestic shipping & import fees.\r\n4.You pay the Transhipper, and they deliver the fish to your address.\r\n???? Combine shipping is available! If you buy multiple fish, contact your transhipper to save on costs.\r\n________________________________________\r\n???? DOA (Death on Arrival) POLICY\r\n•Do Not Open the inner bag: Fish are double-bagged. You must check the fish through the first clear layer. If the inner bag is broken, the warranty is void.\r\n•To Claim: Send a clear photo of the dead fish in the sealed bag via Bettavaro message within 2 hours of delivery (verified by tracking time). No refunds after 2 hours.\r\n•Refund: We only refund the value of the fish (Shipping fees are non-refundable). No returns accepted.\r\n•Our responsibility ends 7 days after marked shipped on Bettavaro, or 3 days after the transhipper delivers to your home.\r\n________________________________________\r\n???? AVAILABLE TRANSHIPPERS LIST\r\nRegion Transhipper Contacts\r\nUSA   : Tucky Hama (CA)\r\nCanada   : Hung Pham, Chuck Bel Espinosa\r\nAustralia   : Jodi-Lea Matheson (QLD)\r\nEU / Germany   : Jan Sassmann, Jasmin Geier (JS Betta)\r\nUK   : Lisa Bradshaw, Dean Hughes (The Betta Box), Siam Betta UK\r\nItaly   : Tania Likhachova (Old House Goldfish)\r\nMexico   : Alberto Morales, Lule Horn\r\nSingapore   : Betta Leong, Iven Betta Shop (Ezekiel Lyon)\r\nMalaysia   : Chee Wiratchaiwan (WcBetta), Patrick Yeoh\r\nPhilippines   : Gerald Prodon\r\nIndonesia   : Mr. Fajar Yulianto, Mr. Ronald Kusuma\r\nVietnam   : Lee Nguyen Amg, Mr. Tran Thanh Tuan\r\nChina / Taiwan   : Jacky Lu, Mr. Jimmy Yeh\r\nHong Kong   : Plakad HK, Betta Miu\r\nSouth Korea   : Kaluta Aqua, Haeri Aqua\r\nJapan   : Ishizu Hiroki\r\nMyanmar   : Wunna Kyaw\r\nUAE / Dubai   : Green Desert Aquarium, Karlo Magno Austria Chio\r\n________________________________________\r\n???? PAYMENT & SHIPPING\r\n• Payment: Managed securely by \r\n                 Payoneer :patchrinpshop@gmail.com \r\n                 Paypal : patchrinpshop@gmail.com\r\n• Shipping: Worldwide from Thailand. Transit takes 11-23 business days to reach your transhipper \r\n(No direct tracking to your home until transhipper reships it).\r\n• Contact: Feel free to contact us via message Bettavaro only. Happy Buying & Bidding!', 'Hybrid / Crossbreed', 'Hybrid / Crossbreed', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'unknown', NULL, NULL, 'AA', 150.00, 'USD', 'Thailand', 'Chiangmai', 'active', 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'available', 6, 0, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '/uploads/listings/41/seller_41_20260517221257_86f765e506ae.jpg', 'Pair Hybrid Alien Copper Betta Fish Male Female M&F Show Quality Live Betta', 'Get this premium M&F Hybrid Alien Copper Betta pair. Healthy, active, and selected from top breeders. Safe shipping with live arrival guarantee. Don\'t miss this unique pair!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0000, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-17 22:00:00', '2026-05-17 22:15:37');
